                "id": 302,
                "name": "RuleText",
                "text": "Rules:\n1. A letter (Cue) appears, followed by another letter (Probe).\n2. If Cue is 'A' AND Probe is 'X': Press RIGHT MIDDLE finger (Target Key).\n3. For ANY other combination: Press RIGHT INDEX finger (Non-Target Key).\n4. ONLY respond after seeing the SECOND letter.\n\nPress SPACE to continue.",
                "startTime": 0,
                "duration": -1,
                "color": "white",
                "font": "Arial",
                "letterHeight": 0.04,
